</button>

    </div>
</section>




        <!-- ✅ Mission & Vision -->
        <section class="section text-center py-4">
            <h2 class="text-danger fw-bold">Our Mission & Vision</h2>
            <p>
                BloodBridge is committed to transforming blood donation in Ghana.  
                Our mission is to save lives by ensuring real-time access to blood in critical moments.  
                We leverage technology and mobilize communities to create a reliable, life-saving network nationwide.
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- ✅ Unique Features -->
        <section class="section text-center my-5">
            <h2 class="text-danger fw-bold">What Makes BloodBridge Unique?</h2>
            <p>
                BloodBridge eliminates outdated, time-consuming methods of finding donors by using a smart location-based system.  
                Our platform instantly connects recipients with available donors nearby, ensuring fast, reliable, life-saving matches.
            </p>
        </section>
            
            



        <!-- ✅ Call to Action -->
<section class="text-center my-5">
  <h2 class="text-danger fw-bold mb-4" data-aos="fade-up">Our Core Values</h2>
  <div class="row justify-content-center g-4">
    
    <!-- Empathy -->
    <div class="col-md-4" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="100">
      <div class="p-4 bg-light rounded shadow-sm h-100">
        <i class="fas fa-hand-holding-heart fa-3x text-primary mb-3"></i>
        <h4 class="fw-bold text-primary">Empathy</h4>
        <p class="text-muted">We prioritize patients and donors, ensuring compassion in every connection.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Reliability -->
    <div class="col-md-4" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="200">
      <div class="p-4 bg-light rounded shadow-sm h-100">
        <i class="fas fa-shield-alt fa-3x text-success mb-3"></i>
        <h4 class="fw-bold text-success">Reliability</h4>
        <p class="text-muted">We deliver timely, accurate matches to help those in urgent need.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Innovation -->
    <div class="col-md-4" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="300">
      <div class="p-4 bg-light rounded shadow-sm h-100">
        <i class="fas fa-lightbulb fa-3x text-warning mb-3"></i>
        <h4 class="fw-bold text-warning">Innovation</h4>
        <p class="text-muted">We harness technology to revolutionize blood donation accessibility.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>


        <!-- ✅ Testimonials -->
        <section class="section text-center my-5 bg-light p-4 rounded">
            <h2 class="text-danger fw-bold">What Our Users Say</h2>
            <blockquote class="blockquote">
                <p>"BloodBridge helped me find a donor within minutes when my family needed it the most. A true lifesaver!"</p>
                <footer class="blockquote-footer">Kwame A.</footer>
            </blockquote>
            <blockquote class="blockquote">
                <p>"As a donor, I love how easy it is to help others. The location-based feature is brilliant!"</p>
                <footer class="blockquote-footer">Ama M.</footer>
            </blockquote>
        </section>

        <!-- ✅ Call to Action -->
        <section class="section text-center my-5">
            <h2 class="text-danger fw-bold">Join Our Mission</h2>
            <p class="lead">
                Help us build a stronger, healthier Ghana. Whether as a donor, volunteer, or supporter,  
                your contribution saves lives.  
            </p>
            <div>
                <a asp-controller="Account" asp-action="SignUp" class="btn btn-danger btn-lg me-2">Become a Donor</a>
                <a asp-controller="Support" asp-action="GetInvolved" class="btn btn-outline-danger btn-lg">Support Our Cause</a>
            </div>
        </section>

    </main>


<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aos@2.3.4/dist/aos.js"></script>
